---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="General Disclaimer — Tony Ciencia" description="Tony Ciencia LLC General Disclaimer — content is educational and informational, not professional advice.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-inner">
      <h1>General Disclaimer</h1>

      <h2>Nature of the Content</h2>
      <p>All content published on TonyCiencia.com — articles, videos, guides, courses, social media comments — is <strong>exclusively educational and informational</strong> in nature. It does not constitute financial, legal, tax, medical or professional advice of any kind.</p>

      <h2>No Guaranteed Results</h2>
      <p>Results mentioned on this site (case studies, testimonials, performance examples) are illustrative and correspond to individual situations. Results vary significantly depending on context, resources, execution and other factors. Tony Ciencia LLC does not guarantee that you will achieve similar results.</p>

      <h2>Use of Information</h2>
      <p>The information published reflects the author's knowledge and opinion at the time of publication. The AI and automation space evolves rapidly; some content may become outdated. Always verify information with current sources before making important decisions.</p>

      <h2>Personal and Professional Decisions</h2>
      <p>For business decisions, investments, legal strategy or any matter that may have significant consequences, we recommend consulting a qualified professional in the relevant field. Tony Ciencia LLC assumes no responsibility for decisions made based on the content of this site.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Tony Ciencia LLC, its employees, collaborators and affiliates will not be liable for losses, direct, indirect, incidental or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use the information published on this site.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For any questions: <a href="mailto:contact@tonyciencia.com">contact@tonyciencia.com</a></p>

      <p class="legal-reviewed">Last reviewed: May 6, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: var(--spacing-16) var(--spacing-6); }
  .legal-inner { max-width: var(--content-width); margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-inner h1 { font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); }
  .legal-inner h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: 600; margin-top: var(--spacing-10); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-reviewed { margin-top: var(--spacing-12); font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--color-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-top: var(--spacing-4); }
</style>
